'''性興奮'''（{{lang-en|Sexual arousal}}），又稱'''性喚起'''，一般是指期待或正在發生[[人类性行为|性行為]]時的[[性欲|性欲]]喚起。人們在[[性交|性交]]前及期間都會出現一系列的身體變化。男性的性興奮會使其陰莖[[勃起|勃起]]。女性的性興奮則會使其[[乳頭|乳頭]]、[[女陰|女陰]]、[[阴蒂勃起|阴蒂]]、[[阴道|阴道]]充血，同時陰道會分泌出[[陰道分泌液|潤滑液]]。像觸摸、體內[[激素|激素]]變化般的[[刺激_(生理学)|生]][[刺激_(心理學)|心理]]刺激會影響性興奮。

性興奮可劃分作幾個階段。人們也不一定因性興奮而去從事性行為，儘管他們已因此而出現一系列的生心理變化。若加以適當[[性愉悅|刺激]]，那麼大多數人的性興奮都會達至其最高峰（[[性高潮|性高潮]]）。人們也可能會追求性興奮本身，即使自己不會達至性高潮。

== 人類的性刺激 ==

[[File:Édouard-Henri_Avril_(5).jpg|thumb]]画家[[爱德华-亨利·阿夫里尔|爱德华-亨利·阿夫里尔]]所绘作品]]

人們會因各種生心理因素而感受到性興奮<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite book|title=Human Sexuality Today|url=https://archive.org/details/humansexualityto0000king_z1e5|year=2014|last=King|first=Bruce M.|publisher=Pearson Education|isbn=978-1-292-04239-8}}</ref>{{rp|70}}。性興奮可因某名人物、該名人物的特定部分，或人類以外的對象而起<ref name="LeVay2012">{{cite book|last1=LeVay|first1=S.|last2=Baldwin|first2=J.|title=Human Sexuality|url=https://archive.org/details/humansexuality0000leva_a7h2|edition=4|year=2012|publisher=Sinauer Associates|isbn=978-0-87893-570-3}}</ref>{{rp|235、485}}。對[[性感帶|性感帶]]的刺激或[[愛撫|性前戲]]皆可讓人感到性興奮<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|last1=Turnbull |first1=O. H. |last2=Lovett |first2=V. E. |last3=Chaldecott |first3=J. |last4=Lucas |first4=M. D.|year=2014|title=Reports of intimate touch: Erogenous zones and somatosensory cortical organization|journal=Cortex|volume=53|pages=146–154|doi=10.1016/j.cortex.2013.07.010|pmid=23993282 }}</ref><ref name="LeVay2012"/>{{rp|259}}，尤其是當心理上對即將發生的性行為有所預期時<ref name="LeVay2012"/>{{rp|525}}<ref>{{cite book|title=Introducing the New Sexuality Studies|chapter=Healing (disorderly) desire|year=2016|isbn=978-1-315-69721-5|editor-last1=Fischer|editor-first1=Nancy L|editor-last2=Seidman|editor-first2=Steven|last=McGann|first=P. J.|publisher=Routledge }}</ref>{{rp|534}}。性興奮可能因為浪漫感受<ref>{{cite book|title=The New Psychology of Love|isbn=978-0-300-11697-7|last1=Sternberg|first1=Robert J. |last2=Weis|first2=Karin|publisher=Yale University Press|year=2006}}</ref>{{rp|50}}、音樂<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Laan | first1 = E. | last2 = Everaerd | first2 = W. | last3 = Van Berlo | first3 = R. | last4 = Rijs | first4 = L. | year = 1995 | title = Mood and sexual arousal in women | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_behaviour-research-and-therapy_1995-05_33_4/page/441 | journal = Behaviour Research and Therapy | volume = 33 | issue = 4| pages = 441–443 | doi=10.1016/0005-7967(94)00059-s| pmid = 7755530 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Mitchell | first1 = W. B. | last2 = DiBartolo | first2 = P. M. | last3 = Brown | first3 = T. A. | last4 = Barlow | first4 = D. H. | year = 1998 | title = Effects of positive and negative mood on sexual arousal in sexually functional males | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_1998-04_27_2/page/197 | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 27 | issue = 2| pages = 197–207 | doi = 10.1023/A:1018686631428 | pmid = 9562901 }}</ref>、令人放鬆的情境<ref>{{cite book|title=Vagina: A new biography|chapter=Your Dreamy Autonomic Nervous System|isbn=9781405517713|last=Wolf|first=N.|publisher=Hachette UK|year=2012}}</ref>而加強。產生性興奮的刺激要素和程度因人而異，也可能隨著時間改變<ref name="Understanding"/>{{rp|230、430}}。

造成性興奮的刺激要素可依接收的感官不同進行分類：包括[[体感|觸覺]]<ref name=":2"/>、視覺<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Karama | first1 = S. | last2 = Lecours | first2 = A. R. | last3 = Leroux | first3 = J. M. | last4 = Bourgouin | first4 = P. | last5 = Beaudoin | first5 = G. | last6 = Joubert | first6 = S. | last7 = Beauregard | first7 = M. | year = 2002 | title = Areas of brain activation in males and females during viewing of erotic film excerpts | url = https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/8355/992195ff7152e295e4e956782cfd33647f39.pdf | journal = Human Brain Mapping | volume = 16 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–13 | doi = 10.1002/hbm.10014 | pmid = 11870922 | pmc = 6871831 | access-date = 2021-05-23 | archive-date = 2017-09-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170914220023/https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/8355/992195ff7152e295e4e956782cfd33647f39.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>、[[嗅觉|嗅觉]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Huh | first1 = J. | last2 = Park | first2 = K. | last3 = Hwang | first3 = I. S. | last4 = Jung | first4 = S. I. | last5 = Kim | first5 = H. J. | last6 = Chung | first6 = T. W. | last7 = Jeong | first7 = G. W. | year = 2008 | title = Brain activation areas of sexual arousal with olfactory stimulation in men: A preliminary study using functional MRI | url = http://www.jsm.jsexmed.org/article/S1743-6095(15)31972-X/fulltext | journal = The Journal of Sexual Medicine | volume = 5 | issue = 3 | pages = 619–625 | doi = 10.1111/j.1743-6109.2007.00717.x | pmid = 18221282 | access-date = 2021-05-23 | archive-date = 2020-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200527170155/https://www.jsm.jsexmed.org/article/S1743-6095(15)31972-X/fulltext | dead-url = no }}</ref>、聽覺<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Levin | first1 = R. J. | year = 1992 | title = The mechanisms of human female sexual arousal | journal = Annual Review of Sex Research | volume = 3 | pages = 1–48 | doi=10.1080/10532528.1992.10559874}}</ref>。包括對話、閱讀、電影、圖像、氣味或環境等，任何能讓人喚起與情色相關的想法或記憶的事物，都是能造成性興奮的情色刺激要素。在大多脈絡下，這些要素可能接著讓人產生進行生理上接觸的欲望，包括[[親吻|親吻]]、[[擁抱|擁抱]]或撫摸性感帶等。人在感到性興奮後也可能渴望刺激身體上較為敏感之部分（例如胸部、[[乳頭調情|乳頭]]、臀部或生殖器等），或直接發生性行為。對於一些人而言，[[戀屁癖|放屁]]<ref>Brenda Love, ''The Encyclopedia of Unusual Sex Practices'', Barricade Books, 1994, p. 118, ISBN 1-56980-011-1</ref>和[[排尿|排尿]]<ref name = Milner2008>{{cite book | editor = Laws DR & O'Donohue WT | last = Milner | first = JS |author2=Dopke CA  | title = Sexual Deviance, Second Edition: Theory, Assessment, and Treatment | publisher = The Guilford Press | location = New York | year = 2008 | pages = [https://books.google.com/books?id=yIXG9FuqbaIC&pg=PA385 384–418] |isbn=1-59385-605-9 |oclc= |doi=| chapter = Paraphilia Not Otherwise Specified: Psychopathology and theory}}</ref>也能带来性兴奋。

性興奮的刺激來源也可能與伴隨其後的性渴望對象無關。例如許多人會因[[裸體|裸體]]或[[色情|色情]]描寫作品而感到性興奮<ref>DeVita-Raeburn, Elizabeth. "[http://www.psychologytoday.com/articles/200512/lust-the-long-haul Lust For The Long Haul] {{Wayback|url=http://www.psychologytoday.com/articles/200512/lust-the-long-haul |date=20210220181043 }}". [[Psychology_Today|Psychology Today]]. 2008-12-26</ref>，其後可能會產生一種非特定的性渴望，並能夠透過性行為獲得滿足。若對物品或人類以外的對象感到性興奮，那麼即可稱為[[戀物|戀物]]或更廣義的[[性欲倒错|性欲倒错]]<ref name="Understanding">{{cite book |title=Understanding human sexuality|last1=Shibley|first1=J.S|last2=DeLamater|first2=John D.|last3=Byers|first3=E. Sandra|isbn=978-1-25-927380-3|year=2018|publisher=McGraw-Hill}}</ref>{{rp|430、434}}。

在一般認知下，女性感到性興奮需要較長的時間。然而科學研究顯示，男性與女性感到性興奮需要的時間並無顯著差異。加拿大[[麥基爾大學|麥基爾大學]]的科學家使用感熱攝影來記錄生殖器附近的溫度變化，藉此來測量達到性興奮所需要的時間。研究員分析每位受測者觀看情色影片或圖片後達到性興奮最高點所需要的時間，發現男性與女性所需的時間幾乎相同，平均約為10分鐘左右<ref name=intro>{{cite web|url=http://edu.love-shop.biz/post/foreplayint.html |title=Your introduction to foreplay |accessdate=2007-05-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070618222527/http://edu.love-shop.biz/post/foreplayint.html |archivedate=2007-06-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而性前嬉所需要的時間則因人而異，也可能受各種因素影響而隨時改變<ref name=intro/>。

與許多其他的動物不同，人類並無[[繁殖季节|繁殖季节]]，因此一整年都可能受性刺激影響感到性興奮<ref name="Dixson2012">{{Cite book|last1=Dixson|first1=A.F|year=2012|url=https://global.oup.com/academic/product/primate-sexuality-9780199676613?cc=fr&lang=en&|title=Primate sexuality: Comparative studies of the Prosimians, Monkeys, Apes, and Human Beings|publisher=Oxford University Press|edition=2nd|access-date=2021-05-23|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814122941/https://global.oup.com/academic/product/primate-sexuality-9780199676613?cc=fr&lang=en&|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

