==== 男性 ====
男性性興奮會令其[[人類陰莖|陰莖]]出現[[勃起|勃起]]。生心理刺激會讓陰莖[[血管舒張|血管舒張]]，最終使得三條海綿體充血（兩條[[陰莖海綿體|陰莖海綿體]]、一條尿道海綿體）。陰莖因此而脹大，並變得堅挺。同時[[阴囊|阴囊]]的皮膚變得繃緊，[[睾丸|睾丸]]提高至接近會陰的位置<ref name="NHS">{{cite web|title=Sexual arousal in men|url=http://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/Goodsex/Pages/Malesexualarousal.aspx|work=NHS Direct|publisher=[[國民保健署|National Health Service]]|access-date=2013-11-03|archive-date=2017-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926180757/http://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/Goodsex/Pages/Malesexualarousal.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，進入興奮狀態的男性不一定會出現勃起——一些40歲以上的男性報稱他們性興奮時不一定會出現勃起<ref>{{cite journal|last=Janssen|first=Erick |author2=Kimberly R. McBride |author3=William Yarber |author4=Brandon J. Hill |author5=Scott M. Butler|title=Factors that Influence Sexual Arousal in Men: A Focus Group Study|journal=Archives of Sexual Behavior |date=2008|volume=37|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s10508-007-9245-5|pages=252–65|pmid=18040768|url=https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/6d8734ea1333fdcc953fecc21c28650b4508a057 }}</ref>。他們亦可以在睡夢當中勃起（[[夜間陰莖勃起|夜間陰莖勃起]]），但這種情況可以在沒出現性興奮的情況下發生。年輕人或性慾旺盛者能夠只靠一閃而過的念頭或途人的一瞬目光，而出現勃起。陰莖在之後亦可能會因為跟衣服的摩擦，而維持一段時間的勃起<ref>{{cite web|title=Embarrassing erections|url=http://www.thesite.org/sex-and-relationships/masturbation/embarrassing-erections-3357.html|work=TheSite.org|publisher=YouthNet UK|access-date=2010-08-10|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410071757/http://www.thesite.org/sex-and-relationships/masturbation/embarrassing-erections-3357.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在持續獲得性刺激，並因此感到興奮的情況下，當事人的[[龜頭|龜頭]]便有機會脹得更大，同時顏色亦會變得更深。睾丸的體積則可在這個時候比原本增加約50%。由於睾丸不斷提高，所以當事人便可能在上述位置及[[會陰|會陰]]感受到暖意。在進一步的刺激底下，受刺激者的心率、血壓、呼吸頻率會上升<ref name="NHS"/>。由於有關刺激會令人全身血流增加，所以一些男性會出現性潮紅<ref>{{cite web|last=Kennard|first=Jerry|title=Sexual Arousal|url=http://menshealth.about.com/od/sexualhealth/a/sexual_arousal.htm|work=Men's health|publisher=About.com|year=2006|access-date=2013-11-03|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906203232/http://menshealth.about.com/od/sexualhealth/a/sexual_arousal.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

再進一步的性刺激會使人達至[[性高潮|性高潮]]，當中骨盆、[[輸精管|輸精管]]、[[前列腺|前列腺]]、[[精囊|精囊]]的肌肉會收縮，迫使精液進入[[尿道|尿道]]。一旦此一過程開始，那麽男性們便很有可能會以[[射精|射精]]收結整套反應。

如果性刺激在高潮前停止，那麽刺激所導致的生理反應會在短時間內消退。若男性們在反复或长时间的刺激底下仍未能達到高潮和射精，那麼他們的睾丸就會變得不舒服<ref>Weinzimer, S.A. & Thorton, P.S., "Blue balls", " ''Pediatrics'' 108(5), 1233-1234", 2001</ref>。

在高潮和射精過後，大多男性都會進入消退期（及在這之上的[[不应期_(性)|不应期]]）。當中他們的陰莖會恢復至疲軟狀態、皮膚潮紅現象消退，並對性失去興趣、感到緩和放鬆——這主要是[[神經激素|神經激素]][[催产素|催产素]]和[[催乳素|催乳素]]的釋放所致的<ref>{{cite journal  |vauthors=Exton MS, Krüger TH, Koch M, etal |title=Coitus-induced orgasm stimulates prolactin secretion in healthy subjects |journal=Psychoneuroendocrinology |volume=26 |issue=3 |pages=287–94 |date=2001 |pmid=11166491 |doi=10.1016/S0306-4530(00)00053-6|url=https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/eb194b5e0370574c39ab5765d9e7221aa6a213c7 }}</ref>。一些年輕男子的消退期可能十分短暫，他們的勃起反應甚至會在某些情境底下不見明顯消退。對於中老年人而言，他們的不應期則可能會維持數小時，甚至數天<ref name="NHS"/>。

====女性 ====
女性性興奮的身體表現有陰道分泌出[[陰道分泌液|潤滑液]]、[[女陰|性器官外部]]充血腫脹、[[陰道|陰道]]内部扩大延长<ref name="Soucasaux">{{cite web|last=Soucasaux|first=Nelson|title=The Female Sexual Response|url=http://www.nelsonginecologia.med.br/femalesexresp_engl.htm|work=Novas Perspectivas em Ginecologia|access-date=2010-08-10|year=1990|archive-date=2019-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121023234/http://www.nelsonginecologia.med.br/femalesexresp_engl.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。研究者已探討了這些反應跟女性主觀性興奮之間在多大程度上相關：大多研究顯示，一些人的性反應跟其主觀性興奮高度相關。而對於另一些人來說，兩者則為弱相關<ref>{{cite journal|last=Rellini|first=Alessandra H.|author2=Katie M. McCall |author3=Patrick K. Randall |author4=Cindy M. Meston |title=The relationship between women's subjective and physiological sexual arousal|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_psychophysiology_2005-01_42_1/page/116|journal=Psychophysiology |date=2005|volume=42|issue=1|pages=116–124|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8986.2005.00259.x|pmid=15720587}}</ref>。

在持續獲得性刺激的情況下，當事人的陰道會分泌更多的潤滑液，[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]和[[阴唇|阴唇]]亦會更為腫脹。由於有關刺激會令更多血液流向皮膚表面，所以上述部位亦會在過程中變紅或變黑。內部變化則有陰道形狀和[[子宫|子宫]]位置改變<ref name="Soucasaux"/>。同時其亦會發生其他生理變化，比如[[心率|心率]]和[[血壓|血壓]]上升、感到臉紅耳熱、震颤（不一定會出現）<ref>{{cite book|last=McKinne|first=Kathleen|title=Sexuality in close relationship|year=1991|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-8058-0719-6|page=59|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4pG9ULmRTRsC|access-date=2013-11-03}}</ref>。

再進一步的性刺激會使人達至[[性高潮|性高潮]]。一些女性在高潮過後不會想再受到進一步的性刺激，她們的性興奮亦很快會消退。因為女性沒有不應期的緣故，故在短時間內可達到二次或多次的性高潮，所以若在這個時候繼續進行刺激，那麼其便可能在短時間內達到第二次或多次的性高潮<ref name="Rosenthal">參見  [http://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153 第133–135頁] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153 |date=20210307014909 }} （有關性高潮的信息）及 [http://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT96#v=onepage&q&f=false 第76頁] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT96#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20210224162858 }} （關於G點与陰部神經的信息）。{{cite book |first=Martha |last= Rosenthal| title = Human Sexuality: From Cells to Society|url=https://archive.org/details/humansexualityfr0000rose | publisher =Cengage Learning|year= 2012| isbn = 0618755713}}</ref><ref name=soc>{{Cite journal| title = The Sexual Response Cycle| publisher = [[University_of_California,_Santa_Barbara|University of California, Santa Barbara]]| url = http://www.soc.ucsb.edu/sexinfo/article/the-sexual-response-cycle|accessdate =2012-08-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725051823/http://www.soc.ucsb.edu/sexinfo/article/the-sexual-response-cycle|archivedate=2011-07-25}}</ref>。但一些來源指出女性亦有不應期——女性也可能在高潮後的一段時間內，不能透過性刺激來使自己興奮<ref name="Schacter">{{cite book| title =Psychology| publisher =Macmillan|year= 2010|page=336|accessdate =2012-11-10| isbn = 1429237198|url = https://books.google.com/?id=emAyzTNy1cUC&pg=PA336|author1=Daniel L. Schacter |author2=Daniel T. Gilbert |author3=Daniel M. Wegner }}</ref><ref name="Weiner & Craighead">{{cite book| title = The Corsini Encyclopedia of Psychology, Volume 2 | publisher =John Wiley & Sons|year= 2010|page=761|accessdate =2012-11-10 |isbn=0470170263 |url = https://books.google.com/?id=pa5vKqntwikC&pg=PA761 |author1=Irving B. Weiner |author2=W. Edward Craighead }}</ref>。

年輕女子的性慾相對較容易喚起，而且她們亦能夠在適當的刺激底下較快達至高潮。不過她們的性反應會隨著年紀增長而出現變化。年紀較大的女性在接受刺激時，一般會分泌出相對較少的潤滑液。研究表明，她們的性滿意度、性行為密度、性慾、性態度、達至高潮的難易度都會在40歲及[[更年期|更年期]]前後發生變化。不过與更年期相比，其他因子有着更大的影響<ref name="sexualityandu.ca"/>。

[[雌激素|雌激素]]的水平下降可能跟陰道乾燥和[[阴蒂勃起|阴蒂在興奮時較難勃起]]有關，但其跟性興趣和興奮並無直接關係。老年女性的骨盆肌肉張力可能會下降，致使其需花更多時間才能從興奮狀態進入性高潮。這可能會令性高潮的強度降低，繼令高潮維持時間減少<ref name="sexualityandu.ca">{{cite web|title=Age-Related Factors that Impact Sexual Functioning|url=http://www.sexualityandu.ca/health-care-professionals/sexuality-in-older-women-and-their-partners/age-related-factors|year=2008|publisher=sexualityandu.ca|access-date=2011-07-12|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621182546/http://www.sexualityandu.ca/health-care-professionals/sexuality-in-older-women-and-their-partners/age-related-factors|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 心理反應 ===
{{see also|性冲动}}
心理上的性興奮涵蓋了對性對象的評量、把對象認定為跟性有關、有關情感反應<ref name="autogenerated2002">{{cite journal | last1 = Basson | first1 = R | year = 2002 | title = A model of women's sexual arousal | journal = Journal of Sex and Marital Therapy | volume = 28 | issue = 1| pages = 1–10 | doi=10.1080/009262302317250963| pmid = 11928174  }}</ref>。认知和生理状态的结合會使人在心理上感到性興奮<ref name="autogenerated2002"/><ref>Chivers, M. L. "[http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.513.4313&rep=rep1&type=pdf Leading comment: A brief review and discussion of sex differences in the specificity of sexual arousal] {{Wayback|url=http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.513.4313&rep=rep1&type=pdf |date=20181010011104 }}", ''Sexual and Relationship Therapy'', 20(4), 377-390, 2005</ref>。一些研究者認為，心理性興奮是认知和经验因子互相影響之結果——有關因子有情感状态、過去经歷、当前的社会环境。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite journal | last1 = Rupp | first1 = H. A. | last2 = Wallen | first2 = K. | year = 2008 | title = Sex differences in response to visual sexual stimuli: A review | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 37 | issue = 2| pages = 206–218 | doi=10.1007/s10508-007-9217-9 | pmid=17668311 | pmc=2739403}}</ref>

==== 男性 ====
男性[[性冲动|性慾]]與性興奮之間的關係相當複雜，一系列因子會增加或減少他們的性興奮<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Janssen | first1 = E. | last2 = McBride | first2 = K. R. | last3 = Yarber | first3 = W. | last4 = Hill | first4 = B. J. | last5 = Butler | first5 = S. M. | year = 2008 | title = Factors that influence sexual arousal in men: A focus group study | url = https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/6d8734ea1333fdcc953fecc21c28650b4508a057| journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 37 | issue = 2| pages = 252–265 | doi=10.1007/s10508-007-9245-5 | pmid=18040768}}</ref>。像[[心率|心率]]、[[血壓|血壓]]、[[勃起|勃起]]般的生理反應往往跟他們報稱的主觀性興奮不一致<ref>Chivers, M.L., Reiger, G., Latty, E., & Bailey, J.M., "[https://www.gaylawnet.com/ezine/gender/sex_difference.pdf A sex difference in the specificity of sexual arousal] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gaylawnet.com/ezine/gender/sex_difference.pdf |date=20180818085417 }}",  ''Psychological Science'' 15(11), 736-744, 2004</ref>。此一現象表明，心理或认知对性興奮有着很大影响。研究者尚未完全搞清男性性興奮的认知層面，不過其的確涵蓋了對性對象的評量、把對象認定為跟性有關、有關情感反應<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Basson | first1 = R | year = 2002 | title = Human sex response cycles | journal = Journal of Sex and Marital Therapy | volume = 27 | issue = 1| pages = 33–43 | doi=10.1080/00926230152035831| pmid = 11224952 }}</ref>。研究表明，像性動機、[[性別角色|性別角色]]期望、性態度般的認知因子會對兩性在主觀性興奮上的差別產生影響。具體而言，男性在觀賞異性[[色情作品|情色影片]]時，較易受到演出者的性別所影響，此外他們也比女性偏向於物化演員<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Rupp|first1=Heather A.|last2=Wallen|first2=Kim|date=2007-08-01|title=Sex Differences in Response to Visual Sexual Stimuli: A Review|journal=Archives of Sexual Behavior|language=en|volume=37|issue=2|pages=206–218|doi=10.1007/s10508-007-9217-9|issn=0004-0002|pmc=2739403|pmid=17668311}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Benson|first1=Etienne|title=The science of sexual arousal|url=http://www.apa.org/monitor/apr03/arousal.aspx|website=American Psychological Association|page=50|date=2003|quote=Another difference has to do with how men react to instances when they can't become aroused. Males who are able to get aroused fairly easily seem unfazed by occasions where they can't get aroused. They tend to attribute it to benign external events--it was something they ate, or they're not getting enough sleep--not as characteristics of themselves. In contrast, men with arousal problems tend to do just the opposite, thinking of every instance of difficulty as a sign of a long-term internal problem, either physiological or psychological.|access-date=2021-05-24|archive-date=2018-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223085344/http://www.apa.org/monitor/apr03/arousal.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在受到性刺激時，男性的[[杏仁核|杏仁核]]和[[下丘脑|下丘脑]]較女性活躍。這表明男性的杏仁核在处理视覺性刺激上有着重要作用<ref name="autogenerated2003"/>。

==== 女性 ====
研究顯示，像性動機、性別角色期望、性態度般的認知因子會對女性主觀性興奮產生重要影響<ref name="autogenerated1"/>。根據巴松（Basson）提出的性反應模型<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Basson | first1 = R | year = 2000 | title = The female sexual response: A different model | journal = Journal of Sex & Marital Therapy | volume = 26 | issue = 1| pages = 51–65 | doi=10.1080/009262300278641 | pmid=10693116 }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated2001">{{Cite journal | doi=10.1080/713846827| pmid=11554199|title = Using a Different Model for Female Sexual Response to Address Women's Problematic Low Sexual Desire| journal=Journal of Sex & Marital Therapy| volume=27| issue=5| pages=395–403|year = 2001|last1 = Basson|first1 = Rosemary}}</ref>，女性對[[亲密关系|亲密关系]]的需求會促使她們參與性刺激活動，令她們產生[[性欲|性欲]]和心理性興奮。心理性興奮亦會影響生理機轉：戈尔迪（Goldey）和范·安德斯（van Anders）<ref>Goldey, K. L., & van Anders, S. M. [https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/bitstream/handle/2027.42/83874/sexy_thoughts.pdf?sequence=1 "Sexy thoughts: Effects of sexual cognitions on testosterone, cortisol, and arousal in women"] {{Wayback|url=https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/bitstream/handle/2027.42/83874/sexy_thoughts.pdf?sequence=1 |date=20170821231355 }}, ''Hormones and Behavior'', 59, 754-764, 2011</ref>的研究顯示，性認知會影響女性的激素水平，比如性意念會使她們體內的[[睾酮|睾酮]]水平急劇上升。研究者表示，杏仁核的反應並不完全由自我報稱的性興奮水平來決定。哈曼（Hamann）等人發現，雖然女性報稱的性興奮水平較男性高，但男性的杏仁核卻比較活躍<ref name="autogenerated2003">{{cite journal | last1 = Hamann | first1 = S. | last2 = Herman | first2 = R. A. | last3 = Nolan | first3 = C. L. | last4 = Wallen | first4 = K. | year = 2003 | title = Men and women differ in amygdala response to visual sexual stimuli | url = https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/b1ab60bc01781ce7f447940274c4bb048fe852a4| journal = Nature Neuroscience | volume = 7 | issue = 4| pages = 411–416 | doi=10.1038/nn1208 | pmid=15004563 }}</ref>。

